Heidi Lenhart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heidi_Lenhart 0 Heidi Noelle Lenhart (born August 22, 1973) is an American actress. She starred as Jenny Garrison in the NBC teen comedy series California Dreams (1992–93) during its first season. Lenhart later went to star in the syndicated television drama Fame L.A. from 1997 to 1998, and had a recurring role in the final season of Fox prime time soap opera Beverly Hills, 90210 (2000). In film, Lenhart played the leading role of Jennifer "Jenny" Caldwell in Au Pair (1999), and its two sequels Au Pair II (2002), and Au Pair 3: Adventure in Paradise (2009).
